1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,960
Oh! Makoto?!

2
00:00:03,170 --> 00:00:04,380
Hey!

3
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:06,760
Makoto!

4
00:00:06,760 --> 00:00:08,050
Haha!

5
00:00:08,050 --> 00:00:09,550
I missed you so much!

6
00:00:09,550 --> 00:00:10,760
Me too.

7
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:12,390
Oh, you...

8
00:00:12,390 --> 00:00:13,760
Ow, ow, ow!

9
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:15,220
Hahaha!

10
00:00:16,640 --> 00:00:17,770
Sorry to drop in on you like this.

11
00:00:17,770 --> 00:00:18,690
No, it's fine.

12
00:00:18,690 --> 00:00:20,850
You startled me, though.

13
00:00:20,850 --> 00:00:21,730
But I'm really glad you're here.

14
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:23,900
Since we haven't seen each other lately...

15
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:25,530
I figured you'd still be awake, so I just came over.

16
00:00:25,530 --> 00:00:26,650
Haha.

17
00:00:26,650 --> 00:00:27,570
Yeah!

18
00:00:27,570 --> 00:00:29,650
I'm sorry to bother you
when you're so busy with work.

19
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:31,450
Aren't you just as busy?

20
00:00:31,780 --> 00:00:33,120
How's your makeup work going?

21
00:00:33,490 --> 00:00:34,330
Actually...

22
00:00:34,330 --> 00:00:35,240
Yeah?

23
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:36,790
The senior stylist I've been assisting

24
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:39,580
asked if I could help out
on another project.

25
00:00:39,750 --> 00:00:40,750
That's amazing!

26
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:41,960
Haha!

27
00:00:42,330 --> 00:00:45,130
And...
it's for a major magazine shoot.

28
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:50,010
I feel like I'm finally catching up to you a bit.

29
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,760
No way. I need to make it big soon

30
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:54,800
so I can request you
as my personal makeup artist.

31
00:00:55,010 --> 00:00:56,060
Thank you.

32
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,680
I'll work hard to become independent

33
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:02,230
so you can trust me completely
with your look.

34
00:01:04,810 --> 00:01:06,190
I'm holding you to that.

35
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:07,570
Me too.

36
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:11,240
I want you to do my makeup
when I stand on stage again.
